desc: Check out our unique designs on cases for iPhone product line. Made of 24k real gold and silver leafs. Each product is a one-of-a-kind artwork from our artisans. Get yours today!

layout.text: Our products are inspired by the traditional lacquer culture of the East, which appeared in China, Vietnam, Korea, Japan. Lacquer technique has been developing and modernizing through many years and contributed to the world of fine art.
